Bruce R. Hazelgrove III
Executive Compensation
As Executive Vice President and Chief Administrative Officer at NEWMARKET CORP, Bruce R. Hazelgrove III made $814,240 in total compensation.  Of this total $442,133 was received as a salary, $350,000 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $0 was awarded as stock and $22,107 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


